Dobby, xDL, BlackReflection, and FreeReflection.

Modifications by SkyShard:
- Re-branded the host UI module from "BlackBox" to "SkyShard" (app name,
  launcher icon, application id, theme colors).
- Pinned NDK to a locally installable version.
- Replaced repository mirrors with google() / mavenCentral() / jitpack().
- Replaced the signing configuration with the american2day shared release
  key so SkyShard APKs sideload alongside other american2day apps.

No engine source files were modified; the SkyShard repository contains
the upstream Bcore, black-reflection, and compiler modules verbatim
(see git history for any future deltas).
